WEBVTT

00:03.030 --> 00:05.870
[Ok Taec-yeon]

00:08.300 --> 00:11.140
[Kim Hye-yoon]

00:14.980 --> 00:17.510
[This program includes
indirect advertisements.]

00:17.580 --> 00:19.850
[Secret Royal Inspector Joy]

00:20.080 --> 00:22.680
[All characters,
organizations, locations,]

00:22.750 --> 00:24.850
[and events in this drama are fictitious.]

00:25.320 --> 00:28.460
[We are looking for a woman named
Sea Goblin living on Ganghwa Island.]

00:25.520 --> 00:32.530
[Previously]

00:28.560 --> 00:29.760
[Mom?]

00:29.860 --> 00:32.729
[Have those three on a boat
and off this island.]

00:32.830 --> 00:34.860
[Are you really Lord Yi-eon?]

00:34.930 --> 00:37.000
Are you really not a ghost?

00:37.070 --> 00:39.900
-Jo-yi!
[-How exactly do you know Jo-yi though?]

00:40.140 --> 00:41.040
[-We are childhood friends.
-We are childhood friends.]

00:41.140 --> 00:44.370
[Park Tae-seo is involved
in the Crown Prince's death?]

00:44.440 --> 00:45.410
[I am sure of it.]

00:45.470 --> 00:48.580
[Chief State Councilor Park Seung
must be dismissed at once.]

00:48.640 --> 00:50.950
-Please dismiss him!
-Please dismiss him!

00:51.010 --> 00:52.480
How dare you arrest me.

00:52.550 --> 00:53.580
[How dare you!]

00:53.650 --> 00:55.420
[What in the world?]

00:55.980 --> 00:57.120
[Arrest him!]

00:58.120 --> 00:59.950
[Episode 11: Abscess Specialist]

01:00.020 --> 01:01.920
[A doctor who specializes
in the treatment of abscess]

01:06.290 --> 01:08.960
[Hwang Bi-ryeong,
Kim Jo-yi, Ra Gwang-soon]

01:08.100 --> 01:12.330
I took the liberty of calculating
our living expenses.

01:12.670 --> 01:16.170
Even if we lead a frugal life
paying our monthly rent,

01:16.240 --> 01:19.340
we will still need 58 nyang 36 jeon
every month.

01:19.910 --> 01:22.480
Then the three of us must earn

01:22.539 --> 01:25.450
-around 60 nyang to make ends meet.
-Right.

01:25.650 --> 01:27.750
I can charge half a nyang
for my fortune-telling.

01:28.120 --> 01:29.750
One client a day--

01:29.820 --> 01:31.620
-It will be 15 nyang.
-Yes, 15 nyang.

01:31.690 --> 01:32.620
Right.

01:32.690 --> 01:35.060
-If I have clients, that is.
-You will.

01:35.590 --> 01:37.289
I have some things to sort out.

01:37.360 --> 01:39.660
Once I am done,
I will find work at a guild.

01:39.729 --> 01:42.030
I can read and am good with numbers,

01:42.130 --> 01:43.470
so a job will easily be offered.

01:44.070 --> 01:46.670
-I will find work as a seamstress.
-Good.

01:46.740 --> 01:50.170
Seung-ryul saved a lot of women
from being scammed like we almost were,

01:50.240 --> 01:52.009
and one of them is a peddler.

01:52.070 --> 01:55.710
I will ask for a job
sewing clothes for noblewomen.

01:55.780 --> 01:58.050
I could put up a flyer at the market
about a clairvoyant fortune-teller.

01:58.180 --> 02:00.010
That sounds like a good idea.

02:00.080 --> 02:02.780
Also put one up about
a talented seamstress.

02:02.850 --> 02:05.390
-Sounds great.
-I will be the one to write them.

02:05.650 --> 02:06.860
-We will put them up.
-We will put them up.

02:06.920 --> 02:08.020
Sure.

02:08.590 --> 02:12.630
[New Real Estates, Selling Dried Fish]

02:11.090 --> 02:13.600
[Ojang-dong Seamstress Jo-yi's
Custom-made Clothes]

02:13.730 --> 02:16.870
[Money will be saved on materials,
but the quality will not be sacrificed]

02:16.930 --> 02:18.130
[with my custom-made clothes.]

02:18.200 --> 02:20.770
[Your figure will be flaunted
to the extreme.]

02:20.900 --> 02:23.440
[Allow me to make your best dress ever.]

02:23.540 --> 02:25.510
-I love it.
-Me too.

02:25.570 --> 02:27.980
[Are you curious about
your husband's past relationships?]

02:28.040 --> 02:31.710
[The clairvoyant Bi-ryeong
will only need to take your hand to know.]

02:31.780 --> 02:34.350
[Allow me to look into
your future for you.]

02:34.650 --> 02:36.850
[-If you have any questions,
-If you have any questions,]

02:36.950 --> 02:38.420
[visit the house in Ojang-dong
with the Chinese trumpet vine.]

02:38.490 --> 02:39.250
[I am Hwang Bi-ryeong.]

02:39.350 --> 02:41.160
-We are done here.
[-And I am Kim Jo-yi.]

02:41.690 --> 02:42.890
They must be new around here.

02:43.530 --> 02:46.090
A seamstress and a fortune-teller?

02:46.800 --> 02:48.400
-Should we pay a visit?
-I want to know

02:48.460 --> 02:50.570
if Young Master Cha and I are compatible.

02:50.630 --> 02:52.630
I needed a new baeja anyway.

02:52.730 --> 02:54.500
We are in luck. Come on.

02:54.600 --> 02:56.170
Did you hear the rumors?

02:56.240 --> 02:58.670
About the Ojang-dong seamstress
by the name of Jo-yi

02:58.870 --> 03:00.040
Yes, I have.

03:00.780 --> 03:02.910
Rumor has it that she matches color well.

03:03.010 --> 03:06.310
A touch of her magic
has women looking sublime.

03:06.450 --> 03:08.450
[Some say she is from Qing.]

03:08.520 --> 03:10.490
[Her skills are beyond
what you will find in Joseon.]

03:10.590 --> 03:13.190
[A seamstress who studied abroad
must surely be different.]

03:16.690 --> 03:19.290
She brings out your curves
with a simple touch.

03:19.360 --> 03:21.930
A woman who had
100 unsuccessful blind dates

03:22.000 --> 03:23.900
found a fiance
after wearing a dress from her.

03:24.000 --> 03:27.570
[Clothes made by Seamstress Jo-yi
make you look slimmer.]

03:27.640 --> 03:29.700
[She has an eye for matching colors]

03:29.770 --> 03:31.070
[to one's skin tone.]

03:31.170 --> 03:33.579
-This one.
-Yes, the color suits you.

03:33.940 --> 03:37.310
I hear you can even
make pigs look beautiful.

03:37.880 --> 03:40.550
The Minister of Personnel's daughter

03:40.620 --> 03:42.050
went on a blind date in a dress you made

03:42.220 --> 03:44.190
which led to her
finding herself a husband.

03:45.350 --> 03:48.820
Right. I was grateful to hear
about the success she had.

03:50.730 --> 03:53.600
They say one's third daughter
is the prettiest of them all,

03:53.829 --> 03:56.160
but my Soo-ryeon failed
her 100th blind date.

03:57.030 --> 03:59.100
If she finally gets engaged
thanks to the dress you make,

03:59.170 --> 04:01.300
I will pay you double.

04:03.370 --> 04:07.610
So please give my girl
the greatest transformation.

04:12.550 --> 04:15.080
Tell me. Do you see any hope?

04:17.050 --> 04:18.390
Go ahead.

04:19.550 --> 04:20.660
Yes, my lady.

04:21.720 --> 04:24.890
First of all,
her dress is too baggy on her.

04:24.990 --> 04:27.800
It is why she looks like
she is hunching over.

04:27.960 --> 04:29.700
The sleeves are too long

04:29.760 --> 04:31.430
and are hiding her beautiful hands.

04:31.570 --> 04:33.770
Judging by her complexion,

04:33.870 --> 04:36.600
rather than a top in cold blueish colors,

04:36.670 --> 04:38.640
she will look better
in a warm pinkish color.

04:38.710 --> 04:41.640
To make her jaw look more V-shaped,
the collar should be deeper.

04:41.710 --> 04:43.540
And rather than a full skirt,

04:43.610 --> 04:45.450
a narrower fit

04:46.010 --> 04:48.580
will bring out her curves more.

04:50.490 --> 04:51.850
[She is ready, my lady.]

05:24.620 --> 05:26.250
Gosh, who am I looking at?

05:26.420 --> 05:27.860
Are you sure you are not an angel?

05:27.920 --> 05:30.090
You are like an angel that has descended.

05:31.030 --> 05:32.990
Goodness, thank you so much.

05:33.060 --> 05:34.800
You have saved this family.

05:34.860 --> 05:36.330
Please do not mention it.

05:39.630 --> 05:40.840
My goodness.

05:40.900 --> 05:42.270
[Did you hear the rumors?]

05:42.340 --> 05:43.810
About the seamstress, I mean.

05:43.940 --> 05:46.010
I hear she is not from Qing.

05:46.270 --> 05:48.380
She reached us from across the galaxy.

05:49.480 --> 05:52.650
Are you saying
she is the reincarnation of Jik-nyeo?

05:52.850 --> 05:55.580
[No wonder her skills
are beyond a human's.]

05:55.650 --> 05:58.390
[-She is a supernatural being.
-Tell me about it.]

05:59.890 --> 06:01.460
[I am amazed.]

06:04.930 --> 06:09.000
I could read your palms
while you wait, you know.

06:22.180 --> 06:24.580
Your husband has a woman on the side.

06:24.650 --> 06:25.780
-A woman?
-Goodness.

06:28.320 --> 06:30.620
-I see long hair.
-Long hair?

06:30.790 --> 06:32.620
-Red lips.
-Red lips?

06:35.690 --> 06:36.920
And two eyes!

06:38.760 --> 06:39.860
Two?

06:40.560 --> 06:41.430
Can you...

06:41.500 --> 06:42.930
One at a time, ladies!

06:43.030 --> 06:44.800
-Who is this wench?
-Let me see.

06:45.030 --> 06:47.000
It seems like you will have a long life.

06:47.370 --> 06:49.370
Bi-ryeong, half a nyang each!

06:51.440 --> 06:53.610
You will be blessed with children
in your later years.

06:53.670 --> 06:55.040
This is a new release.

06:55.110 --> 06:57.050
Do you see the artistry that went into it?

06:57.110 --> 06:59.409
Gosh, your compliments
are making me blush.

06:59.480 --> 07:00.820
You will soon meet your man.

07:01.780 --> 07:03.020
I will reserve these two for you.

07:03.080 --> 07:05.020
-Thank you for this rare gift.
-Thank you.

07:05.590 --> 07:07.120
-We will see you tomorrow.
-Take care.

07:07.720 --> 07:10.290
-Does this feel good?
-Yes, it does.

07:11.090 --> 07:12.490
How much did we make?

07:12.560 --> 07:14.860
You earned 20 nyang
by fortune-telling alone.

07:15.730 --> 07:17.500
Then we can go out tomorrow.

07:17.630 --> 07:20.230
-We will enjoy some bindaetteok.
-Sounds good to me.

07:20.300 --> 07:22.100
Bindaetteok? I second that!

07:22.540 --> 07:24.670
-This is beautiful.
-It has already been sold.

07:26.110 --> 07:27.240
This too.

07:28.040 --> 07:29.110
So they have all been sold.

07:29.180 --> 07:31.580
-Gwang-soon, how much would this be?
-That is 30 nyang.

07:31.680 --> 07:34.120
How much is this? We will soon be rich!

07:39.890 --> 07:43.290
We will get some bindaetteok
and some sirutteok.

07:44.430 --> 07:47.060
I hear that powdered soybean is made daily

07:47.130 --> 07:48.230
due to all the injeolmi
that have to be made.

07:48.300 --> 07:51.170
Not even the throne
can get rid of one's lowly preferences.

07:51.300 --> 07:52.830
It seems that way.

07:53.270 --> 07:55.270
I hear that His Majesty

07:55.340 --> 07:57.740
looks for tidy toenails in women.

07:58.240 --> 08:01.510
He has every court maid and court lady
take their socks off.

08:01.880 --> 08:04.680
Talk about a wild fetish.
Toenails of all things?

08:04.850 --> 08:05.980
That reminds me.

08:06.550 --> 08:07.620
The Minister of Board of War

08:07.680 --> 08:10.020
sent a matchmaker
to Young Master Park Do-soo.

08:10.220 --> 08:11.690
Young Master Park Do-soo?

08:11.920 --> 08:14.890
The only son of Park Seung,
the Chief State Councilor?

08:14.960 --> 08:16.020
Yes.

08:16.320 --> 08:19.390
The family is in the search
of a daughter-in-law.

08:20.190 --> 08:22.500
But I heard he had two sons.

08:22.600 --> 08:25.030
Yes, a bastard son.

08:25.370 --> 08:26.530
Tae-seo is his name.

08:26.830 --> 08:30.000
Lord Park Seung laid hands
on one of his servants.

08:30.240 --> 08:32.970
On the same day at the same hour,
one was born in the master bedroom

08:33.039 --> 08:36.710
while one was born in a servant's quarter.

08:37.610 --> 08:40.049
That must be why
his wife passed away early

08:40.150 --> 08:42.549
from all the pent-up anger.

08:42.620 --> 08:44.750
Even the servant ran away.

08:44.920 --> 08:46.550
She left her four-year-old behind.

08:46.820 --> 08:48.860
The drama, my goodness.

08:49.260 --> 08:50.590
Goodness me.

08:50.790 --> 08:52.760
If you are finished with her,
it is my turn.

08:52.930 --> 08:54.360
Yes, madam.

09:09.310 --> 09:12.850
Young Master, Jo-yi wishes to see you
by the well tonight.

09:12.910 --> 09:14.920
Just you, on your own.

09:14.980 --> 09:16.020
Why is that?

09:16.350 --> 09:19.220
Young Master, by a well
in the middle of the night.

09:19.920 --> 09:21.890
It is perfect for a secret rendezvous.

09:21.960 --> 09:23.020
No, my lord.

09:24.230 --> 09:25.360
Oh, no!

09:36.240 --> 09:38.340
-Hello.
-You made it.

09:38.910 --> 09:39.970
Yes.

09:41.680 --> 09:44.310
Why did you want to meet here,
of all places?

09:45.110 --> 09:47.820
When I met a few noble ladies
to take their measurements earlier today,

09:50.520 --> 09:52.620
I overheard them speak of Lord Park Seung.

10:03.600 --> 10:05.100
-My lord.
-Yes.

10:05.170 --> 10:06.170
There is more.

10:11.510 --> 10:14.240
-Is that so?
-Yes, that is what I heard.

10:15.640 --> 10:18.880
Thank you. Do keep me informed
if you hear anything else.

10:19.380 --> 10:21.020
Sure thing, I will.

10:21.680 --> 10:23.850
I am busy, so I must get going.

10:24.820 --> 10:26.950
What? Wait, but...

10:32.530 --> 10:34.100
I suppose she is very busy.

10:39.930 --> 10:41.440
[Jo-yi wishes to see you]

10:42.140 --> 10:45.740
by the silver grass field today.
Just you, on your own.

10:46.670 --> 10:47.740
Silver grass...

10:48.310 --> 10:50.010
-The silver grass field?
-Gosh.

10:50.510 --> 10:52.480
That is where ghosts appear to haunt you.

10:56.880 --> 11:00.890
Goodness.
Why must we meet at a place like this?

11:09.960 --> 11:11.570
My lord.

11:17.040 --> 11:18.710
My lord.

11:20.840 --> 11:22.140
My lord.

11:24.180 --> 11:25.250
My lord.

11:31.420 --> 11:32.820
-My lord.
-Yes.

11:32.890 --> 11:35.020
Today, I heard some gossip
about Park Do-soo.

11:35.660 --> 11:38.460
Oh, okay.

11:45.570 --> 11:46.800
Is that so?

11:47.070 --> 11:49.770
Yes, that is what I heard. Goodbye, then.

11:49.900 --> 11:51.570
What? Wait, but...

11:54.380 --> 11:55.380
My gosh.

12:02.920 --> 12:04.390
She even does stuff like that now?

12:08.420 --> 12:11.890
Today, she wishes to see you
at the barn by the mill.

12:12.890 --> 12:15.400
The barn? That is where...

12:21.500 --> 12:22.570
Yes.

12:28.940 --> 12:30.140
-My lord.
-Oh, hello.

12:32.050 --> 12:33.950
-Tonight, I must truly...
-My lord.

12:34.580 --> 12:36.680
I heard some gossip about Park Tae-seo.

12:38.120 --> 12:39.220
Park Tae-seo?

12:51.070 --> 12:52.130
Is that so?

12:52.500 --> 12:54.240
Yes, that is what I heard.

12:57.200 --> 12:58.270
Also...

13:14.520 --> 13:17.390
Gosh! My goodness.

13:19.760 --> 13:23.060
No matter how busy you are,

13:23.730 --> 13:26.100
you must make sure
that you are always tidily dressed.

13:26.300 --> 13:28.770
Right, yes.

13:30.870 --> 13:34.610
But then again,
even if you were to wear a straw mat,

13:35.480 --> 13:36.940
you would still look good.

13:39.110 --> 13:41.150
I must go. I have a backlog of orders.

13:41.380 --> 13:43.550
What? But... Wait!

13:43.620 --> 13:44.850
My gosh, I am so busy.

13:48.620 --> 13:52.290
She is very busy, yet again.

14:03.170 --> 14:04.710
[Park Tae-seo is nowhere to be seen.]

14:09.380 --> 14:11.280
This is aconite.

14:11.610 --> 14:13.180
Many know it as an herb, but--

14:13.250 --> 14:14.620
It is also poisonous.

14:14.680 --> 14:18.150
Park Tae-seo,
the illegitimate son of Park Seung,

14:18.520 --> 14:21.120
cultivated large batches of this herb.

14:22.990 --> 14:25.730
Are you saying that the father and son

14:25.790 --> 14:28.360
are involved in the Crown Prince's death?

14:32.330 --> 14:34.400
That is not something
you should say lightly.

14:34.470 --> 14:37.340
Chief State Councilor Park Seung
was the one who installed

14:37.770 --> 14:39.310
the temporary Medicines Department.

14:40.470 --> 14:41.880
A new Medicines Department was installed

14:41.940 --> 14:43.310
and a new abscess specialist
was appointed.

14:45.680 --> 14:47.250
[Aconite, Aconite Plant]

14:46.910 --> 14:50.050
There was a sudden spike
in the prescribing of aconite.

14:51.020 --> 14:54.390
You cannot expect
this to be a coincidence.

14:55.560 --> 14:57.020
I am sure of it.

14:57.460 --> 14:58.560
That day,

14:59.590 --> 15:01.030
the abscess specialist I saw

15:02.230 --> 15:04.130
was in no way an actual physician.

15:05.030 --> 15:06.130
There must have been

15:07.030 --> 15:09.040
another abscess specialist.

15:09.870 --> 15:11.670
Before the interrogation begins,

15:11.770 --> 15:15.440
I will return with evidence
regarding the abscess specialist.

15:15.980 --> 15:17.380
Please put your trust in me.

15:18.910 --> 15:19.950
[Gwanghwamun]

15:32.290 --> 15:33.830
Did you look into it?

15:33.990 --> 15:36.830
I am truly sorry to report

15:36.900 --> 15:38.670
that I could not find any records

15:39.230 --> 15:41.100
on the fake physician you saw that day.

15:42.200 --> 15:44.970
But I did manage to find some information
on the real abscess specialist

15:45.040 --> 15:46.470
who disappeared.

15:48.210 --> 15:50.110
Born in Gyeongsang Province
in the Year of the Horse,

15:50.480 --> 15:51.950
he was an incredibly skilled physician,

15:52.010 --> 15:54.150
so the Crown Prince
trusted him a great deal.

15:55.320 --> 15:57.850
Before the Crown Prince passed away,

15:57.950 --> 16:00.320
he was suddenly dismissed
and vanished from the Palace.

16:07.760 --> 16:10.830
And it seems
that he was a compulsive note-taker.

16:13.530 --> 16:16.970
Then he must have left notes
on the Crown Prince as well.

16:17.740 --> 16:18.770
Yes. He must have.

16:18.840 --> 16:21.510
According to those who saw him
right before his disappearance,

16:23.340 --> 16:25.480
[he acted strangely
and kept having delusions.]

16:25.610 --> 16:27.310
[Then one day,
he left to do a cleansing ritual]

16:27.380 --> 16:30.150
[at Jinin Temple in Mount Samgak.]

16:32.890 --> 16:35.320
[Jinin Temple]

16:41.500 --> 16:43.400
[Buddha]

16:47.400 --> 16:51.470
Then do you think
that the abscess specialist is alive?

16:52.610 --> 16:53.810
Yes, I believe so.

16:57.040 --> 16:58.510
Then we must find him.

16:58.580 --> 17:00.510
Before the investigation begins,

17:00.980 --> 17:02.350
we must find him no matter what.

17:02.420 --> 17:03.680
He holds the key to the solution.

17:11.660 --> 17:12.760
[Buddha]

17:46.790 --> 17:47.830
Giddyap!

17:51.200 --> 17:53.770
I must find him before it's too late.

17:54.440 --> 17:55.540
Giddyap!

18:08.980 --> 18:10.150
Your Majesty.

18:13.350 --> 18:14.560
Your Majesty!

18:17.120 --> 18:20.790
Why is it so hard to play
in peace? Darn it.

18:20.890 --> 18:22.730
My apologies, Your Majesty.

18:23.030 --> 18:25.330
But Lord Park Seung

18:25.430 --> 18:27.900
keeps spouting nonsense behind bars.

18:28.400 --> 18:30.770
Well, that is...

18:56.060 --> 18:57.330
Your Majesty.

18:58.370 --> 19:01.400
What do you mean by the real
abscess specialist is still alive?

19:01.900 --> 19:03.840
You would probably know better...

19:06.240 --> 19:08.980
as to what that means than I do.

19:11.650 --> 19:13.350
How dare you

19:13.580 --> 19:15.520
try to fool me.

19:15.920 --> 19:17.380
I simply...

19:19.050 --> 19:23.690
let Your Majesty know what I only knew.

19:25.160 --> 19:28.230
I was afraid false rumors that the prince

19:28.300 --> 19:30.800
was poisoned would spread.

19:32.170 --> 19:35.600
And that is, by his father.

19:44.310 --> 19:47.920
So you will need me.

19:49.450 --> 19:52.220
Need me to erase
the false rumor that the king,

19:52.290 --> 19:54.590
jealous of the prince who returned home

19:55.460 --> 19:57.520
after suffering
from a foreign country miles away,

19:58.090 --> 20:00.090
poisoned his son.

20:03.160 --> 20:05.000
If you release me,

20:05.600 --> 20:08.670
I will secure your throne again

20:09.440 --> 20:12.070
like I did last time.

20:45.440 --> 20:46.570
Gosh.

20:49.240 --> 20:50.540
How do I...

20:51.580 --> 20:53.450
Darn it.

20:54.050 --> 20:55.380
Will this work?

20:55.680 --> 20:56.720
It hurts!

20:58.090 --> 20:59.390
Goodness.

21:01.190 --> 21:04.290
Darn it. They sure did
a good job of building it sturdy.

21:04.390 --> 21:07.460
They surely used all the tax
from the people to build this.

21:07.590 --> 21:10.560
I embezzled that much grain tax,
but it did not affect

21:10.630 --> 21:13.370
this country's management one bit.

21:15.440 --> 21:19.440
Hey, why are you so calm?

21:19.510 --> 21:20.840
Are you undergoing spiritual training?

21:24.540 --> 21:25.750
You jerk.

21:26.280 --> 21:28.550
How can you fall asleep in this situation?

21:28.820 --> 21:31.720
Tae-seo might make his way down
from the mountains,

21:31.790 --> 21:34.090
but what if he gets arrested as well?

21:36.320 --> 21:37.820
[Go ahead with Mal-jong first.]

21:38.260 --> 21:40.690
The moment you arrive in Ganghwa Island,
hide together with Han-ki.

21:40.960 --> 21:43.260
As Mal-jong said,
even Gokdu might be dangerous.

21:43.960 --> 21:45.070
Please.

21:46.600 --> 21:48.540
What are you saying?
Are you not coming with us?

21:49.170 --> 21:52.240
Go first. I have someone to meet.

21:52.940 --> 21:53.970
Who?

21:55.140 --> 21:56.240
The king.

21:57.640 --> 21:59.480
How on earth can you sleep
right now, jerk? You...

21:59.550 --> 22:00.950
You scared me!

22:01.010 --> 22:02.580
Do not open your eyes so suddenly.

22:02.650 --> 22:04.120
You almost scared me to death.

22:04.180 --> 22:06.850
The way to see the king's face up close.

22:07.690 --> 22:09.720
-What?
-This is what...

22:11.460 --> 22:12.560
Tae-seo meant.

22:12.930 --> 22:14.830
What are you talking about?

22:16.300 --> 22:19.370
What in the world did Tae-seo tell you?

22:26.470 --> 22:28.040
No way.

22:29.940 --> 22:33.210
Are you saying
he will let himself get arrested?

22:37.120 --> 22:38.320
Darn.

22:39.650 --> 22:42.120
So he thought
of meeting the king from jail?

22:44.420 --> 22:45.460
Crazy jerk.

22:55.700 --> 22:58.010
I love the sound of money.

22:58.070 --> 23:01.270
[Jo-yi, I am going to go
to the night market with Gwang-soon.]

23:01.340 --> 23:03.910
-Okay!
[-I am taking Bi-ryeong with me!]

23:04.180 --> 23:06.750
Goodness, Bi-ryeong is on fire.

23:08.020 --> 23:11.820
I wonder who made all these beauties.

23:13.850 --> 23:17.020
I have got lots of both money and orders.

23:17.890 --> 23:19.730
These...

23:20.960 --> 23:23.600
I will set them here.

23:23.730 --> 23:25.070
And this...

23:28.670 --> 23:31.570
will go in my bag as a nest egg.

23:34.270 --> 23:35.310
What?

23:44.620 --> 23:47.850
It would have been great
if you were here with us, Bo-ri.

23:54.130 --> 23:55.230
Jo-yi!

23:56.200 --> 23:57.260
Hey.

24:00.930 --> 24:02.470
What brings you here?

24:03.970 --> 24:05.340
Comb my hair for me.

24:08.410 --> 24:09.480
Sit.

24:18.720 --> 24:21.190
You always used that broken comb,
but this is new.

24:21.350 --> 24:24.060
A lady gave it to me earlier.

24:25.290 --> 24:27.760
That reminds me, she was looking for you.

24:28.400 --> 24:29.800
-Me?
-Yes.

24:29.960 --> 24:32.470
She asked where your house was,
so I told her. Did she not drop by?

24:33.300 --> 24:34.400
No.

24:34.900 --> 24:36.840
No one came by today.

24:37.570 --> 24:38.910
That is strange.

24:39.270 --> 24:41.840
She said she was from
Yeowool Valley, your hometown.

24:46.010 --> 24:47.910
-Yeowool Valley?
-Yes.

24:48.280 --> 24:50.520
She told me you were villagers.

24:52.590 --> 24:54.390
Villagers, I see.

24:55.460 --> 24:57.690
-Did she only mention that?
-Yes.

24:57.890 --> 24:59.530
Yes, villagers.

25:00.260 --> 25:01.630
Villager.

25:02.460 --> 25:03.600
Who can it be?

25:05.500 --> 25:06.830
It hurts, Jo-yi.

25:06.900 --> 25:08.200
My bad.

25:09.100 --> 25:11.100
So do not move.

25:11.200 --> 25:13.370
It will hurt if you do.

25:15.580 --> 25:18.980
You feel like my mom,
combing my hair like this.

25:19.280 --> 25:21.180
Though I would not know that feeling

25:21.280 --> 25:23.650
since I do not have a mom.

25:26.920 --> 25:28.590
You can have that comb.

25:30.620 --> 25:32.630
It was for you,
so why would you give it to me?

25:32.890 --> 25:35.430
You are going to comb my hair anyway,
so what is the big deal?

25:35.760 --> 25:36.960
Just have it.

25:37.130 --> 25:38.570
So that I can drive you hard.

25:40.600 --> 25:44.070
Fine. Drive me hard as much as you want

25:44.140 --> 25:46.540
-since I will comb your hair every day.
-Okay!

26:04.520 --> 26:06.260
[Gunpowder Sales]

26:10.130 --> 26:11.200
[My lord!]

26:13.130 --> 26:14.600
Get back safely.

26:16.570 --> 26:18.140
What is that ledger?

26:20.240 --> 26:22.040
It seems like records of gunpowder sales.

26:22.840 --> 26:23.940
Gunpowder?

26:27.650 --> 26:29.150
[Gunpowder Sales]

26:32.320 --> 26:35.190
[Sea Goblin]

26:35.460 --> 26:37.390
They are extremely persistent,
are they not?

26:38.460 --> 26:41.190
To even cross the sea
and trade at Ganghwa Island.

26:44.060 --> 26:45.970
Give this ledger to Yuk-chil.

26:46.300 --> 26:48.800
I will present it as evidence
when I make a report.

26:51.170 --> 26:53.710
[Gunpowder Sales]

26:55.910 --> 26:58.250
[-Are you home?]
-Yes!

26:58.580 --> 27:00.280
[I brought the house contract.]

27:06.950 --> 27:08.020
Gosh.

27:10.260 --> 27:13.260
Oriental melons must be out of season.
I could not find much.

27:14.160 --> 27:15.530
But I was still able to buy some.

27:15.760 --> 27:18.730
I am such an obedient kid.

27:24.370 --> 27:26.110
Here, the contract.

27:26.770 --> 27:29.240
Right, thanks.

27:30.540 --> 27:32.180
You should at least take a look at it.

27:32.250 --> 27:34.480
No need, I am sure you did a great job.

27:37.480 --> 27:38.690
Then why the long face?

27:40.150 --> 27:42.160
-Are you tired?
-What?

27:44.290 --> 27:46.130
Yes, I am.

27:54.100 --> 27:57.070
As a lawyer, you must have
extensive knowledge of the law.

27:57.240 --> 27:59.410
Right. I probably know
more than you at least.

28:00.370 --> 28:03.440
When an interrogation
by a King's order takes place,

28:03.510 --> 28:05.850
all the evidence must be present

28:06.250 --> 28:07.950
for the offender to be punished, right?

28:08.450 --> 28:09.420
Yes.

28:09.650 --> 28:11.050
Confessions will do,

28:11.120 --> 28:13.220
but having evidence
makes it an easier process.

28:13.950 --> 28:18.290
What will happen if a name appears

28:18.590 --> 28:20.290
on one of the pieces of evidence?

28:23.100 --> 28:24.100
What?

28:25.570 --> 28:28.270
I do not mean the name of anyone guilty.

28:28.600 --> 28:31.640
This person did nothing wrong,

28:31.770 --> 28:35.280
but that person's name is on the evidence.

28:36.010 --> 28:38.410
Could that lead to
the person being punished?

28:39.850 --> 28:42.080
This person must be involved in some way.

28:42.150 --> 28:43.420
A punishment may be too soon,

28:43.720 --> 28:46.950
but the person will be arrested,
tortured, and interrogated.

28:50.090 --> 28:51.590
Why are you asking though?

29:01.770 --> 29:04.500
You may pass. Please step aside.

29:06.970 --> 29:08.340
You may pass.

29:07.810 --> 29:09.980
[Park Tae-seo, Cha Mal-jong,]
[Ji Maeng-soo, Kang Han-ki]

29:10.910 --> 29:12.150
You may pass.

29:12.350 --> 29:14.380
Right. You may pass.

29:16.180 --> 29:17.420
Where are you coming from?

29:18.750 --> 29:20.390
Ganghwa Island.

29:20.450 --> 29:21.550
Ganghwa Island?

29:21.960 --> 29:24.920
Then write down your name and address
on this ledger.

29:25.190 --> 29:26.730
For what reason?

29:27.560 --> 29:30.600
A heinous crime has occurred,
and we are in search of those involved.

29:31.060 --> 29:33.270
It would not be you being a woman and all,

29:33.330 --> 29:34.770
but we are making a list of those

29:34.830 --> 29:37.040
from Chungcheong Province,
Gyeongsang Province, and Ganghwa Island.

29:37.100 --> 29:38.910
Please write down your name.

29:39.070 --> 29:40.070
Of course.

29:41.410 --> 29:42.480
Next.

29:43.310 --> 29:44.740
Stand over here.

29:46.750 --> 29:48.150
You may pass.

29:49.650 --> 29:50.820
-You may pass.
-Thank you.

29:50.880 --> 29:52.720
I do not know how to write

29:52.950 --> 29:54.790
and cannot spell my own address.

29:54.850 --> 29:56.990
-You may pass.
-Thank you.

29:57.390 --> 29:58.630
Stand over here.

29:59.260 --> 30:00.630
Stand behind him.

30:01.800 --> 30:03.330
Write down your name and address.

30:04.600 --> 30:05.800
[Gong Han Ki]

30:11.070 --> 30:12.840
[Gunpowder Sales]

30:12.110 --> 30:14.310
Why on earth is this in your possession?

30:16.080 --> 30:17.340
I do not know.

30:19.410 --> 30:20.750
What do I do?

30:20.950 --> 30:22.780
What if this endangers my mother?

30:25.050 --> 30:28.690
The thought of turning this over to
the Office of Special Justice scares me.

30:29.290 --> 30:32.460
So all of this happened
because you became affiliated

30:32.530 --> 30:34.160
with a secret royal inspector.

30:34.430 --> 30:35.800
A secret royal inspector!

30:37.800 --> 30:39.800
I should have handed this over sooner,

30:41.130 --> 30:42.970
but I broke my promise.

30:43.640 --> 30:46.040
I know that this is wrong, but--

30:46.110 --> 30:49.080
Of course. I understand
your dilemma as her daughter.

30:50.340 --> 30:52.810
However, you will only look guilty too.

30:52.880 --> 30:54.350
You are hiding key evidence.

30:56.650 --> 30:59.320
It will cause trouble
for Inspector Ra as well.

31:01.420 --> 31:03.790
You said the inspector
already read its contents.

31:04.720 --> 31:06.130
Then he might have already

31:06.190 --> 31:08.900
interrogated those involved
and obtained a confession.

31:10.030 --> 31:14.770
Are you saying that my mother
could soon be arrested?

31:14.900 --> 31:17.170
But if she is innocent
like you say she is,

31:17.240 --> 31:18.300
she will be free to leave.

31:20.610 --> 31:23.040
You said that the inspector
acts truthfully and in fairness.

31:23.540 --> 31:25.980
Would he not help her once her innocence

31:26.050 --> 31:27.350
has been proven?

31:30.020 --> 31:34.720
[But what if my mother
is guilty in some way?]

31:36.190 --> 31:37.260
We should go.

31:49.400 --> 31:51.040
Come on, Jo-yi.

31:56.040 --> 31:58.550
No, I cannot possibly do this.

32:03.250 --> 32:05.920
This is why the law is brutal
and ironic in some ways.

32:07.090 --> 32:09.160
We are to honor the three bonds
and five relationships in Confucianism,

32:09.460 --> 32:11.490
but the law sometimes forces us
to violate moral laws.

32:21.100 --> 32:24.570
Then take your time tonight
and think about your options.

32:24.770 --> 32:27.170
You can call me
when you come to a decision.

32:33.880 --> 32:35.920
And have some of this.

32:36.080 --> 32:37.380
You will need the energy.

32:39.550 --> 32:40.550
I will get going then.

33:37.510 --> 33:38.650
My apologies.

33:39.410 --> 33:41.080
Due to all the checkpoints,

33:41.150 --> 33:42.780
I had to take the long route.

33:42.850 --> 33:45.220
Everybody runs late once in a while.

33:45.920 --> 33:47.120
Did you find her?

33:50.990 --> 33:52.560
A friend of hers

33:52.630 --> 33:54.760
helped her find a place to stay.

33:55.760 --> 33:58.670
-A friend?
-Yes, a male friend though.

33:58.970 --> 34:00.830
From what I gathered,

34:00.900 --> 34:02.800
he works as a lawyer in Hanyang.

34:03.800 --> 34:06.470
His name is Choi Seung-ryul.
Does it ring a bell?

34:06.840 --> 34:09.840
Seung-ryul? They are childhood friends.

34:09.909 --> 34:11.210
He is someone we can trust.

34:11.280 --> 34:12.679
Is that so?

34:13.810 --> 34:16.679
Thank you.
The recon must not have been easy.

34:18.320 --> 34:20.350
Because of her good-for-nothing mother,

34:20.620 --> 34:22.560
you had to poke around here and there.

34:22.620 --> 34:24.219
As if that is true.

34:24.290 --> 34:26.659
Even mothers have lives to live first.

34:31.400 --> 34:32.870
You should get going.

34:32.929 --> 34:34.400
Just remember

34:34.469 --> 34:37.239
not to drive an immovable nail
in your daughter's heart.

34:42.580 --> 34:45.080
[Where is it? Tell me where it is.]

34:45.480 --> 34:48.350
[Buddha]

34:46.150 --> 34:48.250
The fact that you are still alive

34:49.179 --> 34:51.380
proves that the promise is still valid.

34:52.449 --> 34:53.690
I do not know where it is.

34:54.889 --> 34:56.760
You were offered something

34:56.820 --> 35:00.830
in exchange for your silence. Where is it?

35:00.990 --> 35:02.800
I have no idea where it is.

35:03.100 --> 35:04.830
Where is it hidden?

35:04.100 --> 35:05.670
[Buddha]

35:25.450 --> 35:27.220
No...

35:36.300 --> 35:37.460
No...

35:38.700 --> 35:42.170
No, you cannot!

35:40.900 --> 35:44.040
[Pharmacy Journal]

35:47.840 --> 35:50.910
No. Please, you cannot.

35:55.410 --> 35:56.550
No...

35:57.120 --> 35:58.820
[In exchange for your silence regarding]

35:58.890 --> 36:01.150
[all that you saw and heard
at the new Medicines Department]

36:01.320 --> 36:02.590
[as well as your cooperation]

36:01.590 --> 36:04.920
[Donggungjeon: Crown Prince's Palace]

36:02.660 --> 36:04.390
[delivering the herbal decoction
served to the Crown Prince,]

36:04.460 --> 36:07.160
[I hereby promise
that I will not threaten]

36:06.590 --> 36:11.600
[Park Seung]

36:07.230 --> 36:10.600
[the life of your daughter
Ra Gwang-soon.]

36:15.070 --> 36:16.700
[Park Seung]

36:32.620 --> 36:33.620
Whoa.

36:52.710 --> 36:55.980
[Sea Goblin]

37:09.460 --> 37:12.630
[Sea Goblin]

37:15.730 --> 37:17.000
Is anyone home?

37:17.700 --> 37:19.030
Hello?

37:25.340 --> 37:26.570
Who is it?

38:11.750 --> 38:12.820
Would you

38:14.720 --> 38:16.620
let me give you a hug?

38:43.620 --> 38:46.650
[Jinin Temple]

38:52.830 --> 38:54.660
[Jinin Temple]

38:56.000 --> 38:57.460
[Buddha]

39:07.610 --> 39:09.480
[Buddha]

39:12.810 --> 39:14.750
[Jinin Temple]

39:24.020 --> 39:25.090
Darn you!

39:47.310 --> 39:48.710
You... How come...

39:59.360 --> 40:01.030
[Pharmacy Journal]

40:12.100 --> 40:14.070
[I have an abscess on my back.]

40:14.370 --> 40:16.810
[What medicinal herbs were used?]

40:17.410 --> 40:19.350
[Aconite, my lord.]

40:49.110 --> 40:50.210
I knew it.

40:51.480 --> 40:53.250
You were the culprit.

40:55.680 --> 40:58.480
You killed the Crown Prince!

40:58.720 --> 41:00.620
-I only--
-Shut your mouth!

41:06.690 --> 41:10.260
All the humiliation I have suffered
for the past year

41:12.930 --> 41:14.570
since the passing of the Crown Prince...

41:16.840 --> 41:19.040
You have no idea.

41:46.930 --> 41:48.030
Get up.

41:55.770 --> 41:58.540
I might feel better
if I killed you right this instant,

42:01.680 --> 42:02.750
but that

42:03.850 --> 42:06.420
would not be enough
to appease the Crown Prince's soul.

42:09.590 --> 42:10.620
Also,

42:11.990 --> 42:14.990
when I am given the chance
to harm someone,

42:18.330 --> 42:20.430
I choose not to abuse that power.

42:21.500 --> 42:22.940
That is

42:24.970 --> 42:26.370
how I exercise

42:28.770 --> 42:29.880
my conscience.

42:30.840 --> 42:32.950
There he is. My lord!

42:39.590 --> 42:40.690
Take him.

43:20.090 --> 43:21.830
When I returned to Joseon,

43:22.600 --> 43:24.360
you were already married.

43:25.200 --> 43:27.270
I heard your husband was
a wealthy middle-class man.

43:29.440 --> 43:32.400
I wished to visit you
when I heard you had returned,

43:33.110 --> 43:34.410
but I could not.

43:35.240 --> 43:38.340
Even if you had visited me back then,
we would not have met

43:39.510 --> 43:40.610
because

43:41.850 --> 43:43.320
I was banished immediately.

43:45.150 --> 43:46.290
I am sorry.

43:46.720 --> 43:48.720
Why are you sorry?

43:49.220 --> 43:51.190
We were just born in the wrong era.

43:58.560 --> 43:59.670
But I thought

44:02.770 --> 44:05.940
you would try to visit me at least once.

44:07.370 --> 44:09.040
Although I was not able to.

44:13.250 --> 44:14.850
Still, I waited.

44:16.050 --> 44:17.150
For you, Mother.

44:24.820 --> 44:26.030
How foolish of you.

44:26.490 --> 44:29.760
You expected that from a mother
who fled to save her own hide?

44:31.330 --> 44:34.970
I understand.
You must have had your reasons.

44:35.300 --> 44:36.600
It does not matter.

44:41.840 --> 44:43.710
By the way,
why did you leave Gyehwa Valley?

44:48.210 --> 44:52.550
To tell you the truth,
I divorced my husband a little while ago.

44:53.950 --> 44:55.090
Good.

44:57.090 --> 44:58.660
You think it is a good thing?

44:59.590 --> 45:02.360
I am certain that you did not
marry him willingly in the first place.

45:04.630 --> 45:08.930
So you think it is okay
for me to live without a husband?

45:11.000 --> 45:13.970
Of course. Do as you wish.

45:17.780 --> 45:20.550
You must learn
to stand on your own two feet.

45:20.850 --> 45:22.180
That is the purpose of life.

45:25.620 --> 45:28.750
We are both alive, and we know that now.
I have nothing more to wish for.

45:30.190 --> 45:32.620
You must have gone through a lot
for the past nine years too,

45:33.030 --> 45:35.060
but I had to put my survival first.

45:35.790 --> 45:38.460
I did my best
to return to you alive like this.

45:38.960 --> 45:40.630
I hope you know that.

45:42.170 --> 45:44.140
How could I not know that?

45:45.140 --> 45:48.770
I am truly grateful
that you are back, Mother.

45:55.110 --> 45:59.020
So forget about me
and move on with your life.

46:01.150 --> 46:04.460
I can no longer live only as your mother.

46:05.720 --> 46:09.560
The truth is,
I no longer wish to live for anyone else.

46:10.000 --> 46:12.500
I want to be alone
and live solely for myself.

46:14.170 --> 46:15.130
Mother.

46:15.200 --> 46:18.040
You are an adult now,
so I need not worry about you.

46:20.340 --> 46:21.840
Sure thing.

46:22.110 --> 46:24.380
I will earn my own living and help you...

46:24.440 --> 46:26.880
I am telling you that I will not stay.

46:29.750 --> 46:31.320
What do you mean?

46:31.450 --> 46:34.850
I came here to see you,
so I have done my duty as a mother.

46:39.760 --> 46:41.590
But... But why?

46:42.330 --> 46:46.370
Are you ill? Or is there another reason?

46:46.470 --> 46:48.670
I can understand. Please tell me.

46:49.300 --> 46:50.740
What I mean is,

46:50.800 --> 46:54.010
I will leave both the name Deok-bong
and past behind.

46:59.910 --> 47:00.950
Why?

47:03.180 --> 47:04.780
Are you going to live as Sea Goblin?

47:15.960 --> 47:17.800
The Office of Special Justice
is looking for this.

47:17.660 --> 47:19.160
[Gunpowder Sales]

47:20.700 --> 47:21.970
And what is that?

47:28.610 --> 47:30.310
This butterfly right here.

47:30.880 --> 47:32.380
It is your mark, is it not?

47:31.080 --> 47:32.480
[Sea Goblin]

47:37.450 --> 47:39.490
This ledger has records
of criminals arrested

47:39.550 --> 47:41.650
by the Office of Special Justice
for trading gunpowder.

47:43.560 --> 47:45.720
So why is your mark here?

47:45.790 --> 47:47.860
How are you connected to them?

47:48.060 --> 47:50.560
Why did you do such dark business
in Ganghwa Island?

47:50.960 --> 47:53.730
What on earth is going on with you?

47:53.800 --> 47:55.630
I am trying to survive.

47:59.910 --> 48:01.010
Do you understand now?

48:01.470 --> 48:04.280
I am trying my best to survive.

48:06.280 --> 48:08.110
So you should wake up

48:08.350 --> 48:10.550
and devote yourself to your future.

48:10.620 --> 48:13.020
And if the Office of Special Justice
is looking for that ledger,

48:13.090 --> 48:15.150
give it to them this instant.

48:15.220 --> 48:17.490
Say that I did.
What if you become a person of interest?

48:17.560 --> 48:20.660
Why would I? Was my name on there?

48:21.930 --> 48:24.430
A butterfly mark cannot
become grounds for anything.

48:24.500 --> 48:27.100
You are the very person who has
that important corroborative evidence.

48:27.770 --> 48:31.070
Or do you want to get arrested
and get in the neck?

48:33.510 --> 48:35.910
That does not answer my question.

48:37.240 --> 48:41.310
I asked if you committed any crimes
with those criminals.

48:42.180 --> 48:43.680
Even if your name is not on it,

48:44.780 --> 48:48.720
I know that mark belongs to you.

48:51.360 --> 48:52.590
I know.

49:05.570 --> 49:07.470
If that bugs you,

49:07.670 --> 49:10.080
commit a crime for me.

49:10.740 --> 49:13.510
If not, uphold justice for yourself.

49:13.710 --> 49:15.180
Choose. That is all you need to do.

49:17.880 --> 49:21.420
Standing on your own from that point on
does not seem to be a bad idea.

50:28.190 --> 50:31.720
Excuse me, is this Gyehwa Valley?

50:31.960 --> 50:33.790
-Yes, it is.
-By any chance...

50:35.060 --> 50:38.930
do you know a lady named Kim Jo-yi
who got married to this village?

50:39.000 --> 50:41.930
I would only know her husband's name
if she got married.

50:42.370 --> 50:44.570
There is no way I would know the name
of another man's wife.

50:48.570 --> 50:49.680
I know her!

50:53.550 --> 50:55.350
I am good friends with her.

50:55.810 --> 50:58.120
What business do you have
with my best friend?

51:00.190 --> 51:02.020
Best friend?

51:05.120 --> 51:07.360
I am Jo-yi's...

51:10.500 --> 51:13.930
I came from Yeowool Valley
to run an errand.

51:14.130 --> 51:15.430
From her hometown?

51:16.970 --> 51:20.610
My goodness, Jo-yi will be thrilled.

51:21.140 --> 51:22.970
Hold on, what do I do?

51:23.040 --> 51:24.740
I am actually on my way to work.

51:25.580 --> 51:26.980
No, that is not important.

51:27.080 --> 51:29.480
-Let me guide you to her right this...
-That is all right.

51:30.050 --> 51:32.350
If you tell me where she is,
I will go myself.

51:32.420 --> 51:34.350
Gosh, in that case...

51:34.850 --> 51:37.090
Go straight,

51:37.160 --> 51:40.860
and when you see the stream, turn right.
Turn right

51:42.960 --> 51:45.100
and take ten steps. After ten steps,

51:45.160 --> 51:46.930
you will see a big tree.

51:47.000 --> 51:50.300
And it is the third house from that tree.

51:50.770 --> 51:52.770
The third.

51:53.540 --> 51:54.640
Thank you.

52:03.250 --> 52:07.090
Ask Jo-yi to braid your hair later.

52:07.220 --> 52:08.590
She is quite good at it.

52:10.560 --> 52:11.790
Have a safe trip.

52:15.760 --> 52:16.800
Ma'am...

52:19.030 --> 52:20.470
The third house.

52:23.900 --> 52:25.900
What are you saying?

52:25.970 --> 52:27.940
You expect me to eat cold food?

52:29.010 --> 52:33.110
The thing is,
I heard my mother was back home now.

52:33.380 --> 52:35.810
I would like to go there
and see her briefly.

52:35.880 --> 52:37.380
What?

52:37.450 --> 52:40.450
She was dragged to Qing.
That is nothing to brag about!

52:40.520 --> 52:42.750
If anything, she should lie low
and not be seen.

52:42.820 --> 52:45.620
Do you want all the neighbors to find out?

52:45.690 --> 52:50.200
"Everyone! I was dragged to Qing,
but now I am back!"

52:50.260 --> 52:51.330
Is that it?

52:51.400 --> 52:53.330
My mother is not a criminal.

52:53.670 --> 52:56.500
I am the one who should be ashamed
of not being able to protect my mother.

52:56.570 --> 52:58.640
Not my mother, for being dragged off.

52:59.540 --> 53:02.170
You have no shame, just like your mother.

53:03.310 --> 53:07.310
Anyway, I do not want to eat right now.

53:07.380 --> 53:08.850
Bring me my lunch later!

53:10.220 --> 53:13.990
I already set the table for you,
so eat when you are hungry!

53:14.050 --> 53:17.190
What? What did you say?

53:17.260 --> 53:19.020
Goodness!

53:19.090 --> 53:21.230
Chu-han!

53:21.290 --> 53:24.460
That wench is trying
to starve her mother-in-law to death!

53:24.900 --> 53:27.930
Chu-han!

53:33.540 --> 53:35.040
That was so mean of her.

53:36.010 --> 53:37.780
How can she say that?

53:40.980 --> 53:43.350
I put up with all her obnoxiousness,

53:43.520 --> 53:45.350
but I cannot if she talks bad
about my mother.

53:46.650 --> 53:48.620
She did not go to Qing
out of her own will.

53:49.390 --> 53:51.990
It is the country's fault we lost the war,
not the women's.

53:52.620 --> 53:55.030
Why do women get blamed for everything?

55:14.910 --> 55:17.910
Look, our lord finally caught him.

55:17.980 --> 55:20.110
Yuk-chil, it is that guy.

55:20.180 --> 55:21.550
You jerk!

55:21.610 --> 55:24.780
Do you know we held a funeral
for our lord because of you?

55:24.880 --> 55:28.120
-You unbelievable jerk!
-Now, now. He is dead meat anyway.

55:32.260 --> 55:35.190
That man over there is our lord.

55:35.330 --> 55:36.900
The Junior Sixth Counselor!

55:36.960 --> 55:40.470
Ra from Naju, Lord Ra Yi-eon!

55:40.530 --> 55:44.100
That man there is our lord!

55:52.880 --> 55:55.810
[Gunpowder Sales]

56:02.590 --> 56:05.560
[Gunpowder Sales]

56:04.660 --> 56:09.260
[Everyone! Our lord is Lord Ra Yi-eon!]

56:09.630 --> 56:12.360
[He has arrested the greatest criminal!]

56:12.430 --> 56:15.430
[Everyone! Our lord arrested
the greatest criminal!]

56:17.470 --> 56:19.370
So it is him.

56:19.440 --> 56:21.610
-Gosh, from stealing to murder.
-Right.

56:21.670 --> 56:24.840
I have never met anyone
so evil in my life.

56:24.910 --> 56:27.850
No wonder the king ordered his arrest.

56:26.340 --> 56:27.850
[Gunpowder Sales]

56:27.910 --> 56:30.050
Guys like him should be beheaded.

56:30.120 --> 56:33.120
Of course. Off with their head!

56:33.180 --> 56:35.020
You wicked jerk!

56:35.090 --> 56:37.320
Stop it.

56:37.390 --> 56:39.460
All criminals should be burned.

56:39.520 --> 56:43.060
What evil things has he done to earn
the title of the greatest criminal?

56:46.970 --> 56:51.540
[Gunpowder Sales]

57:00.310 --> 57:02.080
