containing gunpowder sales.]

57:10.260 --> 57:11.560
[Gunpowder Sales]

57:14.260 --> 57:17.430
[Gunpowder Sales]

57:19.630 --> 57:23.070
[Gunpowder Sales]

57:38.580 --> 57:42.120
[Gunpowder Sales]

57:45.660 --> 57:47.630
