were safely filmed.]

57:59.040 --> 57:59.940
[We thank Lee Jun-hyuk, Jo Kwan-woo,
and Cha Hak-yeon]

58:00.000 --> 58:00.810
[for their special appearance.]

58:01.210 --> 58:03.980
[Secret Royal Inspector Joy]

58:04.610 --> 58:06.210
[I made the wrong choice.]

58:06.540 --> 58:08.810
